metadata.title: RA6, RA8: Which PHY devices are supported from r_ether_phy module in FSP?

sections.content: Which PHY chips are supported from r_ether_phy module in FSP?
Below you can find the list of the PHY devices supported from the r_ether_phy module in FSP.
The r_ether_phy module may need to be customized for PHY devices other than the ones currently supported. Use the existing code as a starting point for creating custom implementation.
